name: Coruscant Guard (V)
Lore: 'Coruscant Guards are an elite force whose assignments include the protection of important political figures, as well as the policing of Coruscant''s higher profile city districts.',
Text: 'Heroic.  Deploys -1 to Senate.  While at Senate, Sidious is cumulatively Politics +2, and, during your control phase, may place this character in Used Pile to take [Virtual Block 5] Expand the Empire into hand from Reserve Deck; reshuffle, or take any one card into hand from Force Pile; reshuffle.',
